title: TV | Apres Match of the Day
text: Last episode in the current series for the hilarious Apres Match lads as the gang takes a sideways look at Ireland's famous win over Louis Van Gaal's Holland at Landsdowne Road in 2001 in their final qualifying match for the 2002 FIFA World Cup in Japan. Plans were then set in motion for what was set to be an epic summer watching Ireland give it there all at the World Cup led by Mick McCarthy with Roy Keane captaining... what could go wrong?
